<div class="oneThirdGrad">
<h3>Documentation</h3>
<p class="intro">
Dig into the documentation.
</p>

<p>
Interchange <a href="#">documentation</a> covers most areas of Interchange use.
</p>
<p>
The documentation includes several guides as well as references to Interchange building blocks such as tags, filters and variables.
</p>

<h4>Quick links:</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="[area download]">Installation instructions</a></li>
<li><a href="[area documentation]">Browse the documentation</a></li>
</ul>

</div>


<div class="oneThirdGrad">
<h3>Mailing lists</h3>
<p class="intro">
Get answers to your questions.
</p>

<p>
Interchange users mailing list holds years of precious knowledge available for your browsing and searching.
</p>

<p>
If you cannot find the answer you were looking for, try asking on the list. You need to be subscribed to the list for posting.
</p>

<h4>Quick links:</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="[area download]">How to ask questions on the mailing list</a></li>
<li><a href="[area download]">Browse mailing list archives</a></li>
<li><a href="[area download]">Subsrcibe to the users list</a></li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="oneThirdGrad">
<h3>Live Help</h3>
<p class="intro">
Chat with Interchange experts.
</p>

<p>
Interchange live help is available as an <a href="#">IRC channel</a> or through <a href="#">Live Help</a>.
</p>

<p>
Interchange experts from around the world gather to discuss Interchange issues and will be happy to answer your questions.
</p>

<h4>Quick links:</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="[area download]">How to request live help</a></li>
<li><a href="[area download]">Live Help</a></li>
<li><a href="[area download]">IRC setup instructions</a></li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="oneThirdGrad">
<h3>Professional support</h3>
<p class="intro">
Get somebody for the job.
</p>

<p>
There are quite a few companies offering expert Interchange help. 
</p>
<p>
If you request help <a href="#">through contact form</a> we will forward your mail to all companies, and they will respond to you personally
</p>
<p>
In case you want to contact a specific company, we hold a <a href="#">list of companies</a> offering professional support. 
</p>

<h4>Quick links:</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="[area download]">Contact form</a></li>
<li><a href="[area download]">Companies offering support</a></li>
</ul>


</div>

